Tencent QQ utilizes the Tencent Device-oriented Service (TDS) Shiply Containing and Distributing Platform to distribute limited-scale gray testing packages based on the QQ account number (uin) and its terminal information. This feature does not guarantee successful retrieval of update data with each request; failure to obtain update data indicates that the entered parameters fall outside the recognized and distributed scope of the Shiply Platform. The QQ Versions Tool makes no warranty regarding the reliability of this feature or any consequences thereof. Please ensure that you have a clear understanding and sufficient capability to bear the associated risks.
